# API Root
GET http://localhost:3000

###
# Get all Gmail messages with pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/gmail?limit=2&offset=0

###
# Get Gmail messages with different pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/gmail?limit=5&offset=1

###
# Get a specific Gmail message by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/gmail/1

###
# Get all Calendar events with pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/calendar?limit=2&offset=0

###
# Get Calendar events with different pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/calendar?limit=5&offset=5

###
# Get a specific Calendar event by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/calendar/1